      • Crop

        public Crop(java.lang.String name,
            int cost,
            int time,
            int xp,
            int minYield,
            int maxYield,
            int salePrice)
        Creates a Crop object with the specified name, cost, time, minimum and maximum yield and sale price.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the crop
        cost - Number of Gold coins required to purchase one bag of seed of the crop
        time - Time in minutes it takes for the specific seed planted to grow to maturity
        xp - Number of Experience Points earned for one unit of crop produced
        minYield - Minimum yield (in units) produced by planting one bag of seed of the given crop
        maxYield - Maximum yield (in units) produced by planting one bag of seed of the given crop
        salePrice - Number of gold coins one unit of produce gives the farmer
